Summary: The data_array property and its associated methods for managing the underlying buffer in StreamPeerBuffer.

PackedByteArray data_array = PackedByteArray()
Method: set_data_array(value: PackedByteArray)
Method: get_data_array() → PackedByteArray

The underlying data buffer. Setting this value resets the cursor. Note: The returned array is copied and any changes to it will not update the original property value. See PackedByteArray for more details.
